Install the AgentOps SDK

pip install agentops

2

Install Crew with AgentOps

pip install 'crewai[agentops]'

3

Add 2 lines of code

Make sure to call agentops.init before calling any openai, cohere, crew, etc models.

import agentops
agentops.init(<INSERT YOUR API KEY HERE>)

Set your API key as an .env variable for easy access.

AGENTOPS_API_KEY=<YOUR API KEY>

Read more about environment variables in Advanced Configuration
4

Run your crew

Execute your program and visit app.agentops.ai/drilldown to observe your Crew! üïµÔ∏è

After your run, AgentOps prints a clickable url to console linking directly to your session in the Dashboard

